<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.9">
<l>māyac cakaṭa mutaittu marutiṟut</l>
<l>tāyar kaḷōṭupō yānirai kāttaṇi</l>
<l>vēyiṉ kuḻalūti vittaka ṉāyniṉṟa</l>
<l>vāyarka ḷēṟṟiṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">vānirai mēyttāṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about the bull of the cowherders who,</l>
<l rend="indent">kicked the deceptive cart, smashed the marutu trees,</l>
<l rend="indent">went with the herders, [and] protected the cow herd,</l>
<l>stood as a sage, playing [his] jeweled bamboo flute!</l>
<l>Jump and sing about he who grazed the cow herd!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
